**Describe your issue**

I am creating a custom set for the box shadow, they can change for different themes. For example, for light and dark.

Configuration:

```css
@import 'tailwindcss';

@custom-variant dark (&:where(.dark, .dark *));
@custom-variant light (&:where(.light, .light *));

@theme {
  --shadow-small:
      0px 0px 5px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02), 0px 2px 10px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06), 0px 0px 1px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
}

@layer base {
  @variant light {
    color-scheme: light;
  }

  @variant dark {
    color-scheme: dark;

    --shadow-small:
        0px 0px 5px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0px 2px 10px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0px 0px 1px 0px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)
  }
}
```

